{
  "texts": [
    "LAMM [5] presents the LAMM-Dataset and framework for scene understanding without alignment stage of 3D point cloud and text.",
    "Valuation MetricsWe measure 3D grounding capability by Accuracy@0.25 and @0.5, which are accuracies of bounding box predictions whose Intersection-over-Union (IoU) w.r.t.",
    "ground-truth box exceeds 0.25 and 0.5, respectively.",
    "Result AnalysisAs the results shown in Table 3, our comparative analysis contains our method against expert models, general 3D-LLMs with the alignment of 3D modality and text, and 3D-LLMs without alignment.",
    "An insightful observation is that our method, based on Vicuna-7b and LLaVA1.5, outperforms 3D-LLMs without alignment, such as LLM-Grounder and LAMM in terms of Acc@0.5."
  ]
}